data.description: Your peaceful, private craftsman style home with incredible 180* city lights, mountain views. Beautiful entry into the greatroom with 11' ceilings, panoramic views. Gas fireplace, builtin entertainment center. One level open floorplan into a gormet kitchen w/granite counters, breakfast bar, double oven, gas cooktop and island. Beautiful woodwork including knotty cedar ceilings, hardwood hickory floors.  Large covered entertaining patio. 3 bdrms+office. Heated tile in kitchen, guest and primary bathrooms. Primary bedroom has access to patio, a large walk-in closet. Primary bath with double vanity, a whrilpool roman tub, a separate walk in shower, enclosed toilet,hook up for bidet. Large finished basement has 9' ceilings, kitchenette/wet bar, walk in storage closet, full bath, has separate entry access to swim spa. Beautiful newer low maintenance landscaping, Slate/flagstone walkways,timed drip sprinklers.Newer fences, security gates. Artesian well has over 100GPM. High-end ATT septic.
